### GET request to example server
GET http://localhost:8083

### GET using Prompt
GET http://localhost:8083/prompts


### GET popular youtubers Prompt
GET http://localhost:8083/prompts/popular?genre=programming


### GET info using instructions Prompt
GET http://localhost:8083/prompts/instruct?userInput=Tell me a Joke about Computers?


### GET songs from parser Prompt
GET http://localhost:8083/parser

### GET List of songs from parser Prompt
GET http://localhost:8083/parser/list

### GET Map of songDTO from parser Prompt
GET http://localhost:8083/parser/map

### GET List of songDTO from parser Prompt
GET http://localhost:8083/parser/dto